{"tid":1620232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對於依家香港好絕望 和理非請入","createTime":"2019-10-04T09:47:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T10:12:23.000Z","uid":315020,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"01e335f4f3c88ab3c2fced5d519ea17e8025772b","tid":1620232,"uid":315020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:47:30.000Z","msg":"我自己對於香港依家既情況 係好絕望同時好嬲<br />\n軍備上前線同對家根本爭一大截<br />\n就算打到狗 都可能比狗開實彈<br />\n更唔講大部份人充唔到人數 見到防暴就跑<br />\n令到前線更加危險<br />\n我知有好多人都有包袱<br />\n怕自己比人拉/屋企有人擔心<br />\n前線何嘗唔係...<br />\n以我自己 仲未有經濟能力 仲係倚靠屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 身邊仲有個女朋友次次擔心 我都好驚自己會有咩事 會比狗拉<br />\n但係 前線為我地滅煙打狗擋子彈<br />\n點解我地唔可以幫下前線 充下場面 帶下魔法液<br />\n<br />\n依家政府仲實行緊急法同宵禁<br />\n雖則見到話有非法集結罪都照出去遊行集會<br />\n但係依家班狗係更加肆無忌彈咁拉你<br />\n<br />\n所以依個時候唔可以絕望<br />\n如果你地仲係自私 擔心自己會有咩後果 而選擇唔出嚟為香港打氣 為前線出一分力 只希望坐享其成 我建議你都係翻大灣區發展 享受大灣區既榮耀<br />\n<br />\n往後既抗爭<br />\n我希望可以做到全民皆兵 和理非都盡量full gear 唔好令前線擔心你地 唔好再見到狗而不斷後退跑 企後少少幫勇武充人數如果你地怕做前線 只要幫前線帶魔法物資就夠<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a484cb00576bc01c1414a31c98b04ff52e0eb7c","tid":1620232,"uid":315020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:47:41.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"f89b09671c2f9275bcacb3c7b32240b5007a1344","tid":1620232,"uid":315020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:47:52.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"fc329b5faba48716f5c3769766f62f94c2e5a5d2","tid":1620232,"uid":315020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:48:02.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"09d9e992178ca4fd4be8bd63ca723753bdcf2549","tid":1620232,"uid":315020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:48:12.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"4fe8df4e3900b09d31618756fb2dcca5755100ec","tid":1620232,"uid":315020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:48:23.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"1a50112d4f9bb99f7eeeba56f3f1b8d7b4e45466","tid":1620232,"uid":315020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:48:33.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"f76f026852d41e2d4a3323eb3816e36e28574f09","tid":1620232,"uid":315020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:48:49.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"1ffc5eb3e2d43159e250b00493f5ff048352c088","tid":1620232,"uid":315020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:49:00.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"eedb730f12abb55936042628b47689ba2494aae0","tid":1620232,"uid":315020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:49:10.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"250dd316280c90f552f5cc7c61a72d36979c35c7","tid":1620232,"uid":315020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:49:20.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"7121e46c24cf4cd590db7a6c8135724a05f00cb0","tid":1620232,"uid":315020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:49:30.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"f3d706334167c67c3d0d32ac24f6aa99e2d08741","tid":1620232,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:50:41.000Z","msg":"和理非絕望係因為冇膽升級 所以先覺得冇野做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beea22d99d196da316722bf83413bce13dde0e46","tid":1620232,"uid":114186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:51:26.000Z","msg":"你老豆係狗"},{"pid":"6832c64b365c5ddf0b4191b504c8ae02a9e32d2e","tid":1620232,"uid":49685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:04:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4afed641ea1521dec03b44d9db4bfe63d0aceffe","tid":1620232,"uid":315020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"beea22d99d196da316722bf83413bce13dde0e46","tid":1620232,"uid":114186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04